    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughhh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……！？　どうした？\n床に倒れ込んだりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura! What’s wrong?\nWhy are you on the floor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.777886298428411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "浮かばない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m stuck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（思わずさくらの体を見る。確かにぴったり床に）\n（くっついたままだ。浮かんではいない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I look at her without thinking. And it turns out she is indeed stuck.)\n(Stuck right to the floor‚ not floating.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.381473978360496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや違う\nさくらは幽霊じゃないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ wait.\nWhy wouldn’t you be stuck to the floor? You’re not a ghost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.381473978360496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい？\n何言ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes?\nWhat are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.548140645027164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアが浮かばないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m stuck‚ as in I’m not getting any ideas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.214807311693832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "自分達の歌ってなんなのかって……\nみんなで考えているんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no idea what “our song” is exactly.\nEveryone’s been brainstorming‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.73659862677258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "…………はあ……もうダメですーー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Argh… It’s just no use.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.56349839369457,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 69.83493963875986,
          "startTime": 32.63333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、落ち着いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ calm down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.113498346010864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "うう、考えれば考えるほど\n分からなくなっていって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but the more I rack my brain‚\nthe more confused I get.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.13016496499381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……頑張ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. We can do this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.57799022515617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.136811188062055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "そういうこと\n苦しめ苦しめ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ that’s what’s going on.\nSuffer‚ suffer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9041580708822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えー、嬉しそう\nもしかして麻奈ちゃんって、いじめっこ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ you look like you’re enjoying this.\nMana‚ are you a bully?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.20415807088222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっぴり、そうかも\nさくらちゃんが苦しんでいる姿、ちょっと可愛いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might have a mean streak in me.\nSakura does look kind of cute when she’s struggling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.79540014829397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんに言いつけちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watch out. I’ll tell Sakura you said that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.72873348162731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.32424372599681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、私のこと呼んだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ did you call me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.35757705933014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……\nなんでもないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ uh…\nIt’s… nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.57478797203458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……\n私、部屋に戻ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…\nI’m going back to my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5747879720346,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1258.5453612987294,
          "startTime": 76.83333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "私も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.90812130536794,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 833.3333333333428,
          "startTime": 79.74145463870128
        }
      ]
    },
    {
