    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "大変そうだけど\n凄く活き活きとしているよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like they’re having a hard time‚\nbut they also seem so vibrant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.92911908394255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "草原に放り出された子馬みたい。右も左も分からなくて\nオロオロしているけど、どこにでも行ける……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re like ponies‚ set wild in the fields. They don’t know left from right‚\nand they’re clumsy‚ but they can go anywhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.91939055289986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……麻奈。さくらが自分の歌を手に入れたら）\n（……恐らく麻奈は……この世界から……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana… When Sakura finds her own song‚)\n(Mana will likely… fade from this world…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7527238862334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9527238862334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんのことはいいの？\n本当に琴乃ちゃんと話さなくていいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure you’re okay with this?\nAre you really okay with not talking to her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.00285999940024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why shouldn’t I be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.53619333273356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
